Module: viorng.sys — virtio-rng entropy device driver. Surfaces
\Device\VirtioRng0 with IRP_MJ_READ; reads return random bytes from
the host hypervisor via the virtio-rng protocol. Links against the
shared virtio.lib (NTOS/VIRTIO).

QEMU device: virtio-rng-pci, vendor 0x1AF4 device 0x1005 (legacy).

!ENDIF

MAJORCOMP=ntos
MINORCOMP=dd

TARGETNAME=viorng
TARGETPATH=$(BASEDIR)\public\sdk\lib
TARGETTYPE=DRIVER

INCLUDES=..\..\inc;..\..\virtio\inc

TARGETLIBS=$(BASEDIR)\public\sdk\lib\*\virtio.lib

SOURCES=viorng.c \
        viorng.rc
